      <b data-is-speakable>Opinion: Iran's Aggression Continues Even Amid Coronavirus And 'Maximum Pressure'</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Hawks argue the Trump administration's approach to Tehran is working, but recent events clearly demonstrate that Iran has not been cowed, argue Ariane Tabatabai and Colin P. Clarke.</b>
